{"tid":2443254,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《蘋果》召喚寫信師 以文字撐手足","createTime":"2021-03-12T02:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T03:10:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"902405301a84bf85a953b6f794a43fe5c3c8e2f9","tid":2443254,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T02:50:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210312/VO3WCUDFAVE33OE4KQCKCBCJLY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210312%2FVO3WCUDFAVE33OE4KQCKCBCJLY%2F&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgwybpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=b77fb788\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210312%2FVO3WCUDFAVE33OE4KQCKCBCJLY%2F&h=0003ac56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210312/VO3WCUDFAVE33OE4KQCKCBCJLY/</a><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》召喚寫信師 以文字撐手足<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MBCVAbsqHAP1gwBtib1nzJT-D1Y=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZUI7IU4Y6RDXTAGFNO6SXNKOCE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMBCVAbsqHAP1gwBtib1nzJT-D1Y%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZUI7IU4Y6RDXTAGFNO6SXNKOCE.jpg&h=8d0da637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n暴政將一場民主派初選定性「顛覆國家政權」，以國安法之名將42人推入囚室，自由無期。誠如黃之鋒親筆信所言，在牢房中跟恐懼及孤寂搏鬥絕不容易，尤其部份人被單獨囚禁，與人溝通的權利亦被剝奪。不少香港人化身「寫信師」，希望一份微小支持，超越高牆穿透鐵窗，溫暖每一位在囚者。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》冀能成為連接高牆內外的窗口，誠邀讀者執筆寫信，向200名在囚手足送上你們的支持，我們挑選後每日在報章刊登，讓失去自由的手足看到你們的心意，累積力量撐下去。<br />\n<br />\n（讀者電郵請發送到letterstoprison@appledaily.com或來函將軍澳工業邨駿盈街8號《蘋果日報》編輯部）"},{"pid":"ab5fe94f0968ddcfcf3069a7fffde5a769457902","tid":2443254,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T03:09:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd0795f33004f1318db868de363adff57f6b6c0","tid":2443254,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T03:10:10.000Z","msg":"冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}